Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.52,0:02:04.29,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}钢琴声
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗨 小贱人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.17,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到能在这里见到你 真叫我激动
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.77,0:02:36.75,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼人君
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.67,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你认识一个穿紫色长裙的人吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.17,0:02:48.64,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是个有着一头长发 美丽的女人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么想要知道那种事
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.51,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.19,0:03:10.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问 你们的母亲
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.97,0:03:12.87,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叫什么名字
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.01,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}科迪莉亚
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫…人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.49,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟了 弄脏了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这件衣服 我还挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为妈妈的血都湿透了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.99,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妈妈的血 真是甜美
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常的 美味
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.75,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还想要更多
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.23,0:05:05.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼人 礼人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.95,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 您怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人…竟敢把我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.78,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弄成这个样子…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.37,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.91,0:05:29.29,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 我早就觉得迟早会变成这样的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.65,0:05:34.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼人 快来救我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人要来了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.29,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他要来杀我了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.64,0:06:02.51,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是绫人君 只是风而已
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.67,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.78,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会保护您的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你把绫人赶走了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 他已经走了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.17,0:06:52.78,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然只有你才是最可靠的啊 礼人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.73,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您最爱的人是我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.29,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您总是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.89,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼人 我爱你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.96,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样您就只属于我了 永远
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.72,0:07:55.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母亲大人 您怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您的胸口开了个洞哦 母亲大人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.43,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}醒醒 母亲大人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.86,0:08:12.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您的心脏在哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.89,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们一起去找吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您是不是死了呀 母亲大人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.13,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都湿透了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母亲大人 您这样会觉得冷吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.12,0:08:38.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我现在就让您暖和起来
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呐 暖和吗 母亲大人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说话呀
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.21,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说您很暖和
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.01,0:09:39.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要 这种地方 我再也待不下去了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以那时候你逃走就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.98,0:09:45.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.74,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.55,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君他们对自己的母亲做了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.99,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那又怎样
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.88,0:10:03.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君 你为什么要给我匕首呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.14,0:10:05.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要缠着我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.81,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再靠近我的话 我就弄坏你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.37,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不仅是你的身体
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.13,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你的心 你的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个在城堡高塔里的女人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是昴君的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.84,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.86,0:10:51.58,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君 好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.95,0:10:53.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放开我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个无力 丑陋而又污秽的我
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又能做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.09,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.27,0:11:24.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴…君
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.16,0:11:26.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}切
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的 好甜
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵死了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}闭嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.39,0:12:24.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你问我为什么要给你银制匕首
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.74,0:12:25.57,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.55,0:12:31.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是为了让你能如我所愿地把它刺进我的身体里
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.59,0:12:34.48,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种事 我怎么可能做得…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.86,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果做不到的话
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.64,0:12:39.41,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就用它了结你自己
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.59,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没有拒绝的权利
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.12,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就如同你不能拒绝被我吸食鲜血一样
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.86,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样就好
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.89,0:13:08.25,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只要安静地 承受我的獠牙就好
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直至永远
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫 绫人君
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要转过来
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.09,0:13:46.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}闭嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.72,0:13:54.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 不准反抗我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.06,0:14:35.20,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除了破坏我什么都不知道 也不想知道
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.47,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被无法抑制的焦躁所煽动
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.69,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沉迷于鲜血的热度 只剩贪欲
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.33,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直至这份饥渴 被满足为止
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.15,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要靠近我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.50,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那会让我想要弄坏你
